Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,两万贯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,足有犯人们听说的重量的千倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那些金子就藏在这北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人的目的和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以把这一点只告诉了我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然总价值仅有日本国家预算的三分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是放到海外 金价就会疯涨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是感觉真的能建立一个国家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手榴弹 有埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那个男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,牛山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谁准你和军队动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不是叫你在那家妓院待命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了白石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了 上马 开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,枪声和爆炸声是前面传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让士兵集合 马也牵过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那边好像在交火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,打死一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(1355.95,129.8)\blur7.5}杀人魔的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:29.60,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)\t(0,500,\c&HFFFFFF&)\blur7.5\pos(1355.95,129.8)}杀人魔的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两个人骑马逃走了 正在追捕当中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个人疑似是有文身的越狱犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他身上没有文身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,难道有人故意报警
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,目的是把我们引出来 抢走文身?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还准备了炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤见中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,方才听到的另一个爆炸声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎发生在堺町大街附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,金融街吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的骚乱是声东击西之计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的目标是银行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再过一分钟就要撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,土方先生 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,据说它辗转到了这里 果然不假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这把钝刀用着就是提不起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,历经数十载 它终于回到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁支行长打开了金库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那刚才的爆炸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,二楼有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,保管贵重品的保险金库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是需要银行的钥匙和客户自己的钥匙才能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人没有去二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,外墙很薄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为了从内部入侵才引发的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抢走了现金 目的应该达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到底想要什么 竟然兵分两路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,保险金库里面就是一些有价证券和珠宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再就是本银行拥有的绘画和刀等美术品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和泉守兼定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,土方岁三!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是那个叫鹤见的军人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好一副天不怕地不怕的面相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然连我的马也偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那个幕末的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是仇视这世道的恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 姑娘们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你也够惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我拜托你们做的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是来过有文身的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 偷出来了 我用新的掉了包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢啦 给 工钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你要那东西干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕藏往茅房下面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,列塔拉也会找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把列塔拉借给你?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 我想和狼交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想剥了列塔拉的皮卖钱喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,列塔拉不是我的东西 不存在借不借的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且今后我不会主动靠近列塔拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想把狼牵扯进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你想干什么 劝你别打它的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么东西软软的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快转棍子 转到不能转为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再抽出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙一身肥膘 看着就好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,白石 要掉下去了 快抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,它没动啊 死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,貉会装死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小心哦 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别被它咬到头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能被它咬到头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,跑了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一点用都没有啊 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,白石就是白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟在我们后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,乖 真听话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是二瓶铁造调教出来的猎犬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,乖 不许咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,闻清楚了 龙 是这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去找哪里还有这种味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看你们还敢不敢说我没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我找的就是这个人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,往积丹的海岸又发现了尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,死者的脑袋被斧头劈开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过先被刀割破了喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,死的是一个捕鲜鱼的外地劳工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,会是那个男人干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,边见和雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个在曰本各地流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了一百多人的杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前在监狱里听他炫耀过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不停留在一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,边走边杀可是逃脱追捕的诀窍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,二瓶铁造虽然也难对付
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是边见和雄的行动完全无法预测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,臭狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然让关节脱臼挣脱出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看我戳爆你的眼珠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,用武器可是耍赖哦 白石小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,别杀他 牛山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亏你能找到这里 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,土方岁三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙别看一脸蠢样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是个妖怪 不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想好了吗 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不杀你是因为你愿意把文身人皮印出来给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在和老头子联手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会想一个人对付整个第七师团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他同伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有个男人号称打不死的杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打不死的杉元?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个诨名有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的搭档吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 与其说是搭档 更像是我的小弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点本事 可是脾气古怪 不好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他基本上不相信我们这些犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要向他提及我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好好利用你的那个保镖就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你或者衫元身上有文身人皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,合作还是厮杀 选一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是和平主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去剥了边见和雄的皮 当做你的诚意如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,渔工?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,雇来捕鲜鱼的季节工人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时期海边会聚集来自各地的工人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,最适合越狱犯藏身了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最近在各处渔场都发生了渔工遇害的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手绝对是一个叫边见的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这么肯定?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每具尸体的后背都会刻上同一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,字?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对他来说 杀人就和呼吸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看着完全是一个普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天他被山里的野猪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,年幼的弟弟在大声哭喊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我却躲在一旁静静地看着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拚命抵抗也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,惨死在不通人性的怪物嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那死法令我毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道他有多么痛苦 多么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,弟弟的眼神渐渐地因绝望失去了光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,每当想起他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就好想杀人 杀谁都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他的文身上有“目”这个字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心舅舅会不会被那个人盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舅舅他们现在去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,准备抓捕食鲱鱼的鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好 杉元 去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吃鲸鱼!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叫边见的犯人说自己对金子没兴趣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是矛盾了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,既然警惕性那么高 为了怕被抓到 四处逃窜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么又留下会吸引其他犯人的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想明白边见的脑子里在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个大恶人更好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以毫不客气地剥了他的文身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沿岸分布着许多大规模的鲱鱼渔场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,打捞上岸的鲱鱼会就地进行加工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,边见和雄可能就混在这些工人当中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.62,Explain,,0,0,0,,阿伊努语 叔伯的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿恰珀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快快快 用力划 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们要干这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,其他科坦的船发现了鲸鱼 朝它射了鱼钩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然后鲸鱼拉着他们从昨天游到了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去帮忙 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是那条船 我们赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.27,Explain,,0,0,0,,阿伊努语 鲸鱼的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看 是芬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,射脖子 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,脖子那里的皮肤更软
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼知道哪里是脖子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好 射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别被甩下船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个季节的海水依然可以冻死人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 鲸鱼冲向那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 要撞过去了 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个光头在喊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有渔工掉海里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的船太大 要回岸边需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不及时烤火取暖 他会因为体温过低被冻死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好 等我把绳子割断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,白石 靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,记得我的那份鲸鱼肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快划 岸边的渔场应该有用来加工鲱鱼的灶火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,掉进海里淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想这么死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这种死法太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和 可算捡了一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,后背最好也烤烤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服也湿透了 脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里脱衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个人毫无疑问就是白石由竹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这位军人估计是他的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定是被我撒的诱饵引到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来找有文身的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 在你们面前 我不好意思脱光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 反而引起他们的怀疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,需要毯子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好人!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是来杀犯人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 这个人身上的味道和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是杀人犯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人会不会把我残忍地杀掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那头吃了弟弟的禽兽一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能主动给别人看文身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这和自杀有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须拚死抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就像弟弟那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 谢谢你们 我好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,换洗的衣服在渔工宿含 我去换
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好想多了解那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你那文身够稀奇的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大白天的 你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的风寒有点重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这宿舍只有渔场的工人才能住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在这里打工 工钱抵房钱行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等下我去问问工头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在集聚场宰杀后像这样晒干的鲱鱼就是“身净鲱鱼”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜鲱鱼不易存放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用这种保存方法就能把它们销往内陆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,榨完油的鲱鱼渣是优质肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们卖得可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚榨完油的大块鲱鱼渣叫粕玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要把它们弄碎这样更容易干燥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,剁碎粕玉要用到这把玉切菜刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,剁这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元 我们还是去找白石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不认识对方的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里闲逛也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那个 吃完饭再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不足以报答你们的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不过热腾腾的白米饭多少拿得出手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,白米饭!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,鲱鱼果然好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,酸味恰到好处 米糠腌菜也带着甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还有白米饭 太奢侈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个搭配欣那了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,欣那欣那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拉欧索玛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘 麻烦你叫方便好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你去旅顺打过仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,杀过人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得杀了几个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,连长相都没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是那些近到能看清脸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是出于罪恶感才忘不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,至少别忘记他们 算是我对那些人的一点补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我有不得不杀了他们的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,相对地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在我快死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我决不会指望自己能安详地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好想让他杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好 杀了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我苦苦追寻的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那他怎么会死在我这种人手里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.93,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}I realize desire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.52,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}And trembling in the anger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:02.60,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Though I know that you're a great liar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:06.27,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}The world is painted in dark grey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}混乱の時代や嘘と暴力の螺旋が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:20.96,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}どうか貴方の未来へと陰落とさぬ様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:28.38,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Going down to reach somewhere together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:34.64,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}もう一度 夢見るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:37.81,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Someday we will find out the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:45.06,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}この傷の数だけ 闇夜を駆け抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.73,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}踊る Long and winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:52.28,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Standing on the cutting edge of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:56.12,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Holding a rusty old knife
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:59.66,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}朝陽が射し示すまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.33,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}駆ける Long and winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.93,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}欲望在我心中咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.52,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}我在愤怒中颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:02.60,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}尽管我知道你是个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:06.27,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}世界却早已被染上一层深灰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}这个混乱的时代 交织着谎言与暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:20.96,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}希望它们不要为你的未来蒙上阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:28.38,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}让我们一起坚持 抵达一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:34.64,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}然后再做一次梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:37.81,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}有一天我们会找到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:45.06,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}有多少伤痕 便跨过多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.73,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}在这条漫长曲折的路上起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:52.28,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}拼搏在生死一线间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:56.12,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}握住那生锈的旧匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:59.66,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}直至晨光洒向大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.33,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}在这条漫长曲折的路上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:20.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,夜を刺す無数の遠吠えが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,天を貫いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:30.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,僕らみんなたった一つの満月に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:35.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,そうやって手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,目的地の消された地図持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,燃える炎 交わし合って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:45.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,荒れた未来図は 続いてるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,痛みもぜんぶ受け取って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:57.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,連れていくんだと 深く胸に誓って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:59.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ぶつかって 傷付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,いつかまた、ここに来るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:04.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,一切の現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,燃え尽きれば美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:13.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,駆け抜ける 白の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:21.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,迷いを捨てた火花が今、散った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:20.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,将夜晚刺穿的无数嗷叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,贯穿了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:30.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,我们大家都向着唯一的满月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:35.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,像这样将手伸出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,拿着被消去目的地的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,燃烧的火焰互相交错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:45.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,未来虽然还模糊 但还是会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕需要承受全部的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:57.23,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,也要将其带走深深地在胸中发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:59.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,历经挫折受过伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,总有一天会再来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:04.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,现实的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,付之一炬 才是美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:13.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,奔跑在这纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:21.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,舍弃迷茫的火花绚烂绽放在这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
